<TEXT>
   Jerry Lewis will play a clothing manufacturer
who gets caught up in a crime scandal in the garment district in
CBS' ``Wiseguy'' this season, executive producer Stephen J. Cannell
said Monday.
   That wasn't the only unusual bit of casting news Cannell had for
reporters at a CBS news conference. The first villain of the
season, a charismatic leader of a white supremacist sect, will be
played by Tennessee attorney Fred Dalton Thompson, best known for
his 1970s television appearances as real-life minority counsel on
