Sissy Spacek. Thompson played himself, the attorney for Marie
Ragghianti, the parole board chairwoman who blew the whistle on a
pardons-for-money scheme. Dalton was later cast as the head of the
CIA in the movie ``No Way Out.''
   Thompson will star in a four-episode storyline. Lewis will guest
star in the next set of episodes.
   Cannell said he decided to offer Lewis the guest shot after he
saw ``The King of Comedy'' again recently. In that film, Lewis had
a rare dramatic role as a famous talk-show host held hostage by an
aspiring comedian (Robert De Niro).
