<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--NationalOpera ADV28-30   10-17 0941</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--National Opera, ADV 28-30,0967</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv28</NOTE>
