<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--Jones ADV28-30   10-17 0857</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Jones, ADV 28-30,0885</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv28</NOTE>
<NOTE>$Adv29</NOTE>
